title: Busta!
sinopse:
Mukai and Soga have been working to pay back debts to the West Side leader, Kishita, when things go awry in their part of town. Not only is a maniac shanking delinquents with impunity, but now the East Side group, Ordine, is also gunning for the West's Vigilante Corps!

(Source: Fallen Syndicate)
